\c 22
\s Ihubo lokubonga kukaDavida
\p
\v 1 UDavida wasekhuluma eN\nd kosi\nd*ni amazwi alelihubo mhla iN\nd kosi\nd* imkhulula esandleni sezitha zakhe zonke lesandleni sikaSawuli\x + Eks. 15.1. Hlu. 5.1. Hlab. 18. 1 Lan. 16.7.\x*.
\v 2 Wasesithi\x + Hlab. 18.2-50.\x*: IN\nd kosi\nd* ilidwala lami\x + Hlab. 31.3. 71.3.\x*, lenqaba yami, lomkhululi wami\x + Hlab. 91.2. 144.2.\x*;
\v 3 uNkulunkulu wedwala lami\x + 22.32,47. Dute. 32.4.\x*, ngizaphephela kuye\x + Heb. 2.13.\x*, isihlangu sami\x + 22.31. Gen. 15.1.\x*, lophondo losindiso lwami\x + Luka 1.69.\x*, inqaba yami ephakemeyo\x + Hlab. 9.9. 46.7,11. 59.9,16,17. 62.2, 6.\x*, lesiphephelo sami\x + Hlab. 59.16. Jer. 16.19.\x*, umsindisi wami; ungisindisile odlakeleni.
\v 4 Ngizabiza iN\nd kosi\nd* edumisekayo\x + 1 Lan. 16.25. Hlab. 48.1. 96.4.\x*, ngakho ngizasindiswa ezitheni zami.
\p
\v 5 Ngoba izinsizi zokufa zingizingelezele, lezikhukhula zobubi zangethusa.
\v 6 Izibopho zesihogo zangigombolozela, imijibila yokufa yayiphambi kwami.
\v 7 Ekuhluphekeni kwami ngayibiza iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngakhala kuNkulunkulu wami\x + Hlab. 120.1. Jona 2.2.\x*; waselizwa ilizwi lami esethempelini lakhe, lokukhala kwami \add kwafinyelela\add* endlebeni zakhe\x + Hlab. 18.6.\x*.
\v 8 Khona umhlaba wazamazama, wanyikinyeka\x + Hlu. 5.4.\x*, izisekelo zamazulu zaqhaqhazela, zazamazama, ngoba wayethukuthele\x + Jobe 26.11.\x*.
\v 9 Kwenyuka intuthu emakhaleni akhe, lomlilo ophuma emlonyeni wakhe waqothula; amalahle avuthiswa yiwo.
\v 10 Wasekhothamisa amazulu, wehlela phansi\x + Hlab. 144.5. Isa. 64.1.\x*; lomnyama onzima wawungaphansi kwenyawo zakhe\x + Eks. 20.21.\x*.
\v 11 Wasegada \w ikherubhi\w**, waphapha, wabonakala phezu kwempiko zomoya\x + Hlab. 104.3.\x*.
\v 12 Wasemisa umnyama \add waba\add* ngamadumba inhlangothi zonke zakhe\x + Jobe 36.29.\x*, lokuqoqana kwamanzi, amayezi amnyama omkhathi.
\v 13 Ekukhazimuleni okuphambi kwakhe kwavuthiswa amalahle omlilo.
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yaduma isemazulwini\x + 1 Sam. 2.10. 7.10. Jobe 37.4. Hlab. 29.3. Isa. 30.30.\x*, loPhezukonke walikhupha ilizwi lakhe.
\v 15 Yathuma imitshoko\x + Dute. 32.23. Hlab. 7.13. 77.17. 144.6. Hab. 3.11.\x*, yabachitha; imibane, yabaphaphathekisa\x + Josh. 10.10.\x*.
\v 16 Khona kwabonakala imisele yolwandle, kwembulwa izisekelo zomhlaba, ekusoleni kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 106.9. Nah. 1.4. Eks. 15.8.\x*, ekuvutheleni komoya wamakhala ayo.
\p
\v 17 Iphezulu yathuma, yangibamba\x + Hlab. 144.7.\x*, yangenyula emanzini amanengi\x + Eks. 2.10.\x*.
\v 18 Yangophula esitheni sami esilamandla, kwabangizondayo, ngoba babelamandla kulami\x + 22.1.\x*.
\v 19 Babephambi kwami osukwini lwenhlupheko yami, kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yaba yisisekelo sami\x + 22.6.\x*.
\v 20 Yangikhuphela endaweni ebanzi\x + Hlab. 31.8. 118.5.\x*, yangikhulula, ngoba yayithokoza ngami\x + 15.26.\x*.
\p
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* yangivuza njengokulunga kwami\x + 22.25. 1 Sam. 26.23. 1 Kho. 8.32. Hlab. 7.8.\x*, yangibuyisela njengokuhlanzeka kwezandla zami\x + Hlab. 24.4.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba ngizilondolozile indlela zeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Gen. 18.19. Zaga 8.32.\x*, kangisukanga kuNkulunkulu wami ngenkohlakalo.
\v 23 Ngoba zonke izahlulelo zayo zaziphambi kwami\x + Hlab. 119.30,102.\x*, lezimiso zayo, kangiphambukanga kuzo.
\v 24 Njalo ngangiqondile phambi kwayo\x + Gen. 17.1.\x*, ngizinqandile ebubini bami.
\v 25 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* ingibuyisele njengokulunga kwami\x + 22.21.\x*, njengokuhlanzeka kwami phambi kwamehlo ayo.
\p
\v 26 Kolesihawu uzaziveza ulesihawu; koqotho uzaziveza uqotho\x + Mat. 5.7.\x*;
\v 27 kohlanzekileyo uzaziveza uhlanzekile; lakophambukileyo uzaziveza uphambukile.
\v 28 Labantu abahlutshwayo uzabasindisa\x + Eks. 3.7.\x*, kodwa amehlo akho aphezu kwabaziphakamisayo, uzabehlisela phansi.
\v 29 Ngoba uyisibane sami, N\nd kosi\nd*, iN\nd kosi\nd* izakhanyisa-ke ubumnyama bami.
\v 30 Ngoba ngawe ngigijimile \add ngadabula phakathi\add* kwebutho, ngoNkulunkulu wami ngeqe umthangala.
\p
\v 31 UNkulunkulu; indlela yakhe iphelele; ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lihloliwe\x + Hlab. 12.6. 119.140. Zaga 30.5.\x*; uyisihlangu kubo bonke abaphephela kuye\x + 22.3. Hlab. 17.7.\x*.
\v 32 Ngoba ngubani onguNkulunkulu ngaphandle kweN\nd kosi\nd*? Njalo ngubani olidwala ngaphandle kukaNkulunkulu wethu\x + 1 Sam. 2.2. Isa. 45.5,6. Dute. 32.31,39. Hlab. 86.8.\x*?
\v 33 UNkulunkulu uyinqaba yami \add l\add*amandla\x + Hlab. 27.1. 28.8. 31.4.\x*, owenza indlela yami iphelele\x + Jobe 22.3. Hlab. 101.2,6. 119.1.\x*.
\v 34 Owenza inyawo zami zibe njenge\add ze\add*zimpala\x + 2.18. Hab. 3.19.\x*, wangimisa ezingqongeni zami\x + Dute. 32.13. 33.29. Isa. 58.14.\x*.
\v 35 Ofundisela izandla zami impi, ukuze idandili lethusi ligotshiswe zingalo zami\x + Hlab. 144.1.\x*.
\v 36 Unginikile lesihlangu sosindiso lwakho, lokuzithoba kwakho kungikhulisile.
\v 37 Wenze laba banzi inyathelo lami ngaphansi kwami, ukuze inqagala zami zingatsheleli\x + Zaga 4.12.\x*.
\p
\v 38 Ngixotshene lezitha zami ngazibhubhisa, kangibuyanga ngaze ngaziqeda.
\v 39 Ngaziqeda, ngazigwaza, ukuze zingavuki; kodwa zawa ngaphansi kwenyawo zami.
\v 40 Ngoba ungibhincise amandla kusenzelwa impi\x + Hlab. 18.32,39.\x*, wabakhothamisela phansi kwami abangivukelayo\x + 22.49. Hlab. 44.5.\x*.
\v 41 Unginike intamo yezitha zami, labo abangizondayo ngababhubhisa\x + Gen. 49.8. Eks. 23.27. Josh. 10.24.\x*.
\v 42 Bakhangela, kodwa engekho umsindisi; eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kodwa kayibaphendulanga\x + Jobe 27.9. Zaga 1.28. Isa. 1.15.\x*.
\v 43 Ngasengibacholisisa\x + Eks. 30.36. Jobe 14.19.\x* njengothuli lomhlaba\x + 2 Kho. 13.7.\x*, ngabagxoba njengodaka lwezitalada\x + Mika 7.10. Zek. 10.5. Isa. 10.6.\x*, ngabatsahaza\x + Gen. 1.6. Hlab. 18.42.\x*.
\p
\v 44 Wasungikhulula ekuphikiseni kwabantu bami\x + 19.9,43. 20.1,2,22.\x*, wangigcina ngiyinhloko yezizwe\x + 8.1-14.\x*; abantu enganginga\add b\add*azi bangisebenzela\x + Isa. 55.5.\x*.
\v 45 Abezizweni bazazehlisela phansi kimi; bangenela ukuzwa ngendlebe bazangilalela.
\v 46 Abezizweni bazabuna, baphume ezinqabeni zabo\x + Mika 7.17.\x* bethuthumela\x + Hlab. 76.10.\x*.
\v 47 IN\nd kosi\nd* iyaphila; njalo kalibusiswe idwala lami, kaphakanyiswe uNkulunkulu, idwala losindiso lwami\x + Hlab. 95.1. Dute. 32.15. Hlab. 89.26. Hlab. 18.46.\x*;
\v 48 uNkulunkulu onginika impindiselo, lowehlisela izizwe ngaphansi kwami\x + Hlab. 144.2.\x*;
\v 49 longikhupha ezitheni zami; laphezu kwabangivukelayo wena wangiphakamisa\x + 22.40. Hlab. 59.1.\x*; lemuntwini wodlakela wangikhulula\x + Hlab. 140.1.\x*.
\v 50 Ngenxa yalokhu ngizakudumisa, N\nd kosi\nd*, phakathi kwezizwe, ngihubele ibizo lakho indumiso\x + Roma 15.9. Hlab. 18.49.\x*.
\v 51 Ingumphotshongo wosindiso kuyo inkosi yayo\x + Hlab. 144.10.\x*, isenzela ogcotshiweyo wayo umusa\x + Hlab. 89.20.\x*, kuDavida, lenzalweni yakhe kuze kube nininini\x + 7.12,13,29. Hlab. 89.29.\x*.